{"tid":535071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩中年運輸工猝死　一為順豐速運員","createTime":"2018-01-20T12:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T14:15:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52b21b0b1ae19d74bbcf3ace69b27f0cd84db022","tid":535071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180120/20280196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F20280196&d=E75aot0gCfojnsAZZOEX83Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=0257a511\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F20280196&h=14b92c06\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180120/20280196</a><br />\n<br />\n兩中年運輸工猝死　一為順豐速運員<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】兩名中年運輸工人昨先後疑因心臟病猝死，其中一人為順豐速運員工，昨晨工作期間突然暈倒，送院不治。另一名運輸工則為沒有上班，工友登門探訪時發現他猝死家中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180120/large/20la7p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F20la7p04.jpg&h=4ff0b263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順豐速運員工作期間疑心臟病發猝死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順豐︰將安排緊急援助金<br />\n<br />\n猝死的順豐速運員工姓郭（52歲），昨晨10時許，他在青衣航運路36號亞洲物流中心順豐大廈工作期間，突然不適暈倒，工友見狀報警。救護員到場替事主急救再送院搶救，惟最終返魂乏術。據悉事主患有冠心病，疑心臟病突發猝死。就有員工猝死，順豐香港回應指對事件深表惋惜，向其家屬表示最深切慰問，並將安排恩恤金及緊急援助金，同時會繼續與家屬保持緊密溝通，進行後續跟進工作。<br />\n<br />\n另一名42歲猝死工人獨居荃灣老圍富昌徑黃宜合村一單位，據悉他近日曾透露身體不適，但一直沒有求醫，工友昨晨見他沒有上班，於早上近10時登門探訪，發現他昏迷屋內，立即報警，救護員到場證實他已死亡，毋須送院，警方調查後相信是病發失救致死，並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁瑞帆"},{"pid":"47c3b3f2525835f617a69880d4992de5f2ca7554","tid":535071,"uid":137627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T12:58:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">另一名運輸工則為沒有上班，工友登門探訪時發現他猝死家中。<br />\n</span><br />\n一唔見人就上門睇咩事，原來香港仲有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e41aaa101bc34da8f1f79fb2539863ab2e039c","tid":535071,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"順豐速遞，做撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0530f7600e1c5125bad5b4d10cd593bcfc0dde52","tid":535071,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:07:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9eeef120fef11b705afbccccdb81e1d263a8fe9b","tid":535071,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:07:38.000Z","msg":"幾時先會立法限制每日最高工時？"},{"pid":"ebfbd51cb166bddb52c55944623656a572f8afed","tid":535071,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9eeef120fef11b705afbccccdb81e1d263a8fe9b","tid":535071,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:07:38.000Z","msg":"幾時先會立法限制每日最高工時？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"caebb6fac893823bf30f4e91ae1895ef82b2c6b0","tid":535071,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eeef120fef11b705afbccccdb81e1d263a8fe9b","tid":535071,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:07:38.000Z","msg":"幾時先會立法限制每日最高工時？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:15:18.000Z","msg":"運輸真係冇得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送得哂就可以早放<br />\n送唔哂堆住啲貨喺度又係死，仲會畀客屌死"}]}